    <text>
        <body>
            <div type=”letter”>
                <opener><dateline><date when="1916-09-05">Sep. 5, 1916.</dateline></date>
                    <salute>Dear <persName key="harriet_monroe">Harriet</persName>:</salute></opener>
                <p> I am delighted to know that you are taking/<persName key="richard_aldington">Aldington&apos;s<add place="above"></add></persName> <!--not sure this is nested properly --> <title key="beautyUnpraised" level="a">&quot;Beauty Unpraised&quot;</title> and <title key="ave" level="a">&quot;Ave.&quot;</title> Will you be so kind as to send me back the other two manuscripts which you do not want, as I want to try to sell them elsewhere.</p>
                <persName key="dh_lawrence">Lawrence&apos;s</persName> address is;
                <placeName key="england">
                    Higher Tregerthen,
                    Lennor,
                    St. Ives,
                    <placeName key="cornwall"> Cornwall </placeName>,
                    England.
                    </placeName>
                    <p>Good luck to your vacation!</p>
                <closer>Affectionately yours,</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
